Alonzo is good here, covering a lot of topics with lots of laughs. I would also recommend 'Tall, Dark, and Funny', it was good, too.

Alonzo Bodden is a funny and insightful comic. Intelligent humor is rarely heard these days. Enjoyed this dvd immensely. He talks about topics that make you think and then say "Yeah, I remember that".

Don't sleep on this DVD. Translation, BUY IT. The true meaning of LOL. Buy one for yourself then pick up another for a friend. Funny, Honest and intelligent. Good clean humor. Makes you laugh then makes you think then makes you want to watch it again and again. Only bad thing about it was that it had to end.

Alonzo Bodden knocks one out of the park with this special. Clever, witty, and hilarious! He covers a wide range of topics from current events, to dating and travel. A great compilation and dynamite delivery. The bit about the veterinarian had me in stitches!
Great comedy from start to finish. Subject matter very insightful and entertaining ! A must see comedy routine ! Jokes are fresh and to the point !

I enjoyed his sets on Last Comic Standing, and I saw all the positive reviews of this DVD saying that he was funny without being crass, so I bought this, but I wished he hadn't used so much foul language. I was unprepared for it, and didn't care for it. Disappointed. I was expecting more like what I saw of him on NBC, but I guess I forgot how much the censors change things for network TV. I wish the DVD material had been more like his network material, which I really liked.
